  "Description": {
    "English": "Insert <span class=\"name name-stellar\">bait or lures</span> to attract <span class=\"name name-technology\">specific fish</span>, or to improve <span class=\"name name-technology\">catch chances</span>. Note: any foodstuff may be used as bait.<br><br>Current Bait: <%NAMETAG%>%BAIT%<><br>Catch Rarity Improvement: <%RARETAG%>%RARE_BOOST%%<><br>Catch Size Improvement <%SIZETAG%>%SIZE_BOOST%%<><br>Other notes: <%TAG%>%NOTES%<>",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "嵌入<span class=\"name name-stellar\">诱饵与鱼饵</span>以吸引<span class=\"name name-technology\">特定种类的鱼</span>或者提升<span class=\"name name-technology\">捕获几率</span>。注意：所有食物都能被用作诱饵。<br><br>当前诱饵：<%NAMETAG%>%BAIT%<><br>稀有鱼类捕获几率提升：<%RARETAG%>%RARE_BOOST%%<><br>捕获尺寸提升<%SIZETAG%>%SIZE_BOOST%%<><br>其他注意事项：<%TAG%>%NOTES%<>",
    "TraditionalChinese": "放入<span class=\"name name-stellar\">誘餌或假餌</span>可以吸引<span class=\"name name-technology\">特定魚類</span>或增加<span class=\"name name-technology\">捕獲機會</span>。注意：任何食物都可以當作誘餌使用。<br><br>目前誘餌：<%NAMETAG%>%BAIT%<><br>漁獲稀有度提升度：<%RARETAG%>%RARE_BOOST%%<><br>漁獲大小提升度：<%SIZETAG%>%SIZE_BOOST%%<><br>其他說明：<%TAG%>%NOTES%<>"
